## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [pip5k4 pip5k5]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Pollen harvested from pip5k4 pip5k5 mutants germinates at a lower rate than wild type pollen, and pollen tube growth is slowed. However, the general shape of the pollen tubes is normal.
   - [pip5k5]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;pip5k5 mutants do not show any obvious defects in pollen germination or pollen tube growth. But, these processes are compromised in pip5k4 pip5k5 double mutants.
